{"tid":55407,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【二戰紀念】Watershed Hong Kong － The Living Monuments","createTime":"2016-12-26T11:17:00.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T11:24:23.000Z","uid":26671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"31541c86b784f20e96dfe713811101c28fac73bb","tid":55407,"uid":26671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T11:17:00.000Z","msg":"為紀念香港保衛戰 75 周年，Watershed Hong Kong 仿傚英國傳統，發起 The Living Monuments 活動，各大媒體俱已廣泛報道。就像攝影的今昔重疊技術，有心人重踏先烈腳步，讓歷史重現人世之中。<br />\n<br />\n別以為飾演軍人，不過換換衣服。他們都投身鍛鍊，學習步操，才能寓致敬於行動。且看他們下過的苦功。<br />\n<br />\n（內有小小笑點。筆者一樣左右不分，望勿介意）<br />\n<br />\n「我地想同大家講，75 年前有批人為左保衛香港而犧牲」<br />\n<br />\n........<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/15676127_797442067061407_2136867146289325706_o_P5VBF_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F15676127_797442067061407_2136867146289325706_o_P5VBF_1200x0.jpg&h=e752f12e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/watershed-hong-kong-the-living-movements/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fwatershed-hong-kong-the-living-movements%2F&d=%2FAZ6MBPf8Rv6qfnvzqptvaEBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=06b0d4bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fwatershed-hong-kong-the-living-movements%2F&h=772de5db\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/watershed-hong-kong-the-living-movements/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e2fa14298e7812aefd686683aa12772eccaf9f8","tid":55407,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T11:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba14d1b01c74916a8c5be3ceef84551e5c4d5284","tid":55407,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-